      <title>拉贾帕称美联储不急于降息</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-06-13/fed-is-in-no-rush-to-cut-rates-rajappa-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[法国兴业银行的 Subadra Rajappa 和瑞银的 Jonathan Pingle 讨论了美联储下一步可能采取的行动。Rajappa 表示不急于降息，而 Pingle 则表示美联储非常乐意等待降息。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-06-13/fed-is-in-no-rush-to-cut-rates-rajappa-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 13 Jun 2024 13:38:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
